block content
    main.house.house--thames
        section.house__hero
            .house__hero__container-top
                .house__hero__image
                    img(src="/images/house/thames.jpg")
                .house__hero__image-mobile
                    img(src="/images/house/thames.jpg")
                .container
                    .row
                        .col-24.col-md-14.offset-md-5.house__hero__col
                            .house__hero__container
                                p.house__hero__text house
                                h2.house__hero__title Thames
            .house__hero__container-bottom
                .container
                    .row
                        .col-24.col-md-22.offset-md-1
                            .row
                                .col-24.col-md-16
                                    .house__hero__wrapper
                                        p.house__hero__location-text.house__hero__location-text--dark House Thames - Thames, 1300
                                        p.house__hero__location-text Palermo Soho
                                .col-24.col-md-8
                                    .house__hero__wrapper
                                        a.house__hero__button(href="/book-now") Book now
        section.house__description
            .container
                .row
                    .col-24.col-md-22.offset-md-1
                        .row
                            .col-24.col-md-16
                                h2.house__description__title The house
                                p.house__description__text Its located in the famous Thames street, in PALERMO neighborhood, the most popular for students and young people. Just in the middle of two important subway lines (“A” red and “D” green) that conects all the city. Several bus lines nearby. Supermarket, cafés, bank and 24hs store 1/2 blocks away.
                                p.house__description__text It is a newly renovated coliving home with 2 floors + terrace. It is spacious and bright and totally equipped. It has 11 rooms so you will share your experience with other colivers from all around the world. Couples or 2 friends are welcome to share 1 private room, too. There are 3 shared bathrooms with shower, sink and toilette.
                                p.house__description__text The kitchen it is full equipped with fridge and freezer, stove, owen, microwave, toaster and all utensils for cooking and eating. There is a dinning table where to share your meals with your new friends.
                                p.house__description__text The living room has a sofa to relax and a round desk where you can study or just spend some time with your computer.
                                p.house__description__text Two of the guests favorite areas are open spaces where you are allowes to smoke: a beautiful intern patio next to the entrance and a big terrace in the higher floor. It is equipped with a large table and lounge chairs to enjoy your free time in the sun.
                            .col-24.col-md-8
                                .house__description__container
                                    .house__description__wrapper
                                        .house__description__icon
                                            img(src="/images/house/location-icon.png")
                                        p.house__description__wrapper-text
                                            span Location
                                            |Palermo Soho

                                    .house__description__wrapper
                                        .house__description__icon
                                            img(src="/images/house/bed-icon.png")
                                        p.house__description__wrapper-text
                                            span Rooms
                                            |11

                                    .house__description__wrapper
                                        .house__description__icon
                                            img(src="/images/house/shower-icon.png")
                                        p.house__description__wrapper-text
                                            span Shared Bathrooms
                                            |3
